content: Ok, here's what I saw. This time, you went much more carefully through the document whereas last time you started slowly and then speeded up after goals. Execution logs and platform development are ones you came up with, so only you know those. ai_workflows is not in the document I sent you, we must have skipped that one or i didn't put it in the database. Here is a screenshot of those fields. These iterations are taking a lot of time. Is it faster to get you connected to Firestore so you can directly access and configure? How do we solve this?
